Package: BTdecayLasso
Type: Package
Title: Bradley-Terry Model with Exponential time Decayed log-likelihood and Adaptive Lasso
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Zhou Yunpeng, Xu Jinfeng
Maintainer: Zhou Yunpeng <michael_zhou_hku@gmail.com>
Description:  We apply Bradley-Terry Model to estimate teams' ability in paired comparison data. Exponential Decayed Likelihood function is applied for dynamic approximation of current rankings and Lasso penalty is applied for variance reduction and grouping.
Imports: optimr, ggplot2, stats
